parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt to retract properly can lead to loose or hanging seat belts, which can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident. Additionally, damaged seat belt assemblies can compromise the overall safety of the vehicle.
symptoms: The seat belt does not retract
the seat belt hangs loose
the seat belt gets caught in closing doors
the seat belt does not retract when exiting the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt system can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident, as the seat belt may not provide adequate protection or restraint.
symptoms: The seat belt allows the occupant to sustain injuries
the seat belt does not provide adequate protection
the seat belt allows the occupant to be projected forward
the seat belt does not function as intended.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can lead to the seat belt becoming unfastened, which can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle unfastens when tapped from behind
the seat belt becomes unfastened during normal use.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the frame can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, leading to potential safety risks, such as loss of control or collapse of the vehicle, especially in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Rust holes in the frame
severe rust coverage on the frame
frame corrosion
weakened frame structure.

symptoms: The vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel is off-center
the tie rods are frozen
the steering rod is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure of Dealership to Complete Recall Repairs
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the dealership to complete the recall repairs can lead to a delay in fixing the safety issue, potentially causing accidents or other safety hazards.
symptoms: The dealership fails to complete the recall repairs
the consumer is told that the part is not available
the consumer is charged for additional repairs not related to the recall.
